nodes.text: Tahbotza was a male Dug who worked for Sebolto during the waning years of the Galactic Republic. In 32 BBY, he was wanted by the Malastare Special Service for attempting to blackmail members of Senator Ask Aak's staff. His last known location was at the outskirts of Pixelito City. His bounty, worth 3,000 credits alive and 1,500 dead was claimed by Jango Fett.
